ReportQuery.ReportQueryText:
<QueryBundle> <QueryText>select * from ( select fsm.ByUserGID ,u.LastName + ', ' + u.FirstName as 'UserLastFirstName' ,dateadd(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as 'StartDT' ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,hii.InventoryItemName ,fhl.LocationName ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(mi.TargetAFOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty' ,0 as 'AdjustedAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'ActualAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty_Error' ,0 as 'AdjustedAF_MQty_Error' ,it.TransactionType ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(coalesce(hi.LoadToleranceOz, ing.LoadToleranceOz), hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'Tolerance_MQty' ,hc.CompanyName ,KeyValue = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID from InventoryTransaction it join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi on mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID = it.TransactionSourceGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join HistoryInventoryItem hii on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Ingredient ing on ing.InventoryItemGID = ii.InventoryItemGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ii.CompanyGID left join HistoryIngredient hi on hi.HistoryIngredientGID = (select top 1 hi2.HistoryIngredientGID from HistoryIngredient hi2 where hi2.HistoryInventoryItemGID = hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID order by hi2.CreatedDT desc) join HistoryLocation fhl on fhl.HistoryLocationGID = it.FromHistoryLocationGID join HistoryCompany hc on hc.HistoryCompanyGID = hii.HistoryCompanyGID left join [User] u on u.UserGID = fsm.ByUserGID where it.TransactionType = 4 union all
select usr.UserGID ,usr.LastName + ', ' + usr.FirstName as UserLastFirstName ,MIN(d.StartDT) as 'StartDT' ,fs.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,null as InventoryItemName ,thl.LocationName ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(d.TargetAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(d.AdjustedAF_Oz), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AdjustedAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(d.DropAF_Oz) , cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'ActualAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(d.DropAF_Oz) - d.TargetAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty_Error' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(SUM(d.DropAF_Oz) - SUM(d.AdjustedAF_Oz), cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AdjustedAF_MQty_Error' ,d.TransactionType ,0 as 'Tolerance_MQty' ,hc.CompanyName ,KeyValue = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID from ( select fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID ,thl.HistoryLocationGID ,drop_trans.TransactionType ,drop_trans.StartDT ,drop_trans.TargetAF_Oz ,adjustedAF.AdjustedAF_Oz ,drop_trans.DropAF_Oz from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID
cross apply (select DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT) as 'StartDT' ,it.TransactionType ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,SUM(it.TargetUnitQuantity) as 'TargetAF_Oz' ,SUM(it.UnitQuantity) as 'DropAF_Oz' ,PartialDropNumber = ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by it.TransactionSourceGID order by it.TransactionDT) ,PartialDropCount = COUNT(1) over (partition by it.TransactionSourceGID) from InventoryTransaction it where it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID and it.ToLocationGID = fsd.LocationGID and it.TransactionType = 1 group by it.TransactionSourceGID, it.TransactionDT, it.DurationSeconds, it.ToHistoryLocationGID, it.TransactionType) drop_trans join HistoryLocation thl on thl.HistoryLocationGID = drop_trans.ToHistoryLocationGID outer apply (select top 1 da.FeedingScheduleDropGID ,da.FeedingScheduleDropAdjustmentGID ,da.AdjustedAFOz ,da.AdjustedDMOz from FeedingScheduleDropAdjustment da where da.FeedingScheduleDropGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID and da.AdjustmentDT <= drop_trans.StartDT order by da.AdjustmentDT desc) da outer apply (select case when drop_trans.PartialDropNumber = drop_trans.PartialDropCount then da.AdjustedAFOz else drop_trans.DropAF_Oz end as 'AdjustedAF_Oz') adjustedAF where drop_trans.TransactionType = 1 ) d join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID = d.FeedingScheduleDropGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join Location dl on dl.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = dl.CompanyGID join HistoryLocation thl on thl.HistoryLocationGID = d.HistoryLocationGID join HistoryCompany hc on hc.HistoryCompanyGID = thl.HistoryCompanyGID left join [User] usr on usr.UserGID = fsd.ByUserGID group by fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID, usr.UserGID, usr.LastName, usr.FirstName, fs.InstanceDate, thl.LocationName, d.TargetAF_Oz, cmp.MediumMeasurementType, d.TransactionType, hc.CompanyName ) z where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
ReportQuery.SQLStatement:
select * from (select fsm.ByUserGID ,u.UserID as 'UserName' ,u.FirstName ,u.LastName ,u.LastName + ', ' + u.FirstName as 'UserLastFirstName' ,it.TransactionDT ,CONVERT(datetime, convert(date, dbo.GetInventoryTransactionReportDT(it.InventoryTransactionGID))) as 'ReportDate' ,hii.InventoryItemName ,fhl.LocationName as 'Location' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(mi.TargetAFOz, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty' ,0 as 'AdjustedAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'ActualAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty_Error' ,0 as 'AdjustedAF_MQty_Error' ,it.TransactionType ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(hi.LoadToleranceOz, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'Tolerance_MQty' from InventoryTransaction it join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi on mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID = it.TransactionSourceGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join HistoryInventoryItem hii on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID join HistoryIngredient hi on hi.HistoryInventoryItemGID = hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID join HistoryLocation fhl on fhl.HistoryLocationGID = it.FromHistoryLocationGID join HistoryCompany hc on hc.HistoryCompanyGID = hii.HistoryCompanyGID left join [User] u on u.UserGID = fsm.ByUserGID
union all
select fsd.ByUserGID ,u.UserID as 'UserName' ,u.FirstName ,u.LastName ,u.LastName + ', ' + u.FirstName as 'UserLastFirstName' ,it.TransactionDT ,CONVERT(datetime, convert(date, it.TransactionDT)) as 'ReportDate' ,null as InventoryItemName ,thl.LocationName as 'Location' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.TargetAFOz, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(da.AdjustedAFOz, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AdjustedAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.ActualAFOz, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'ActualAF_MQty' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.ActualAFOz - it.TargetAFOz, hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF_MQty_Error' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.ActualAFOz - isnull(da.AdjustedAFOz, it.TargetAFOz), hc.MediumMeasurementType) as 'AdjustedAF_MQty_Error' ,it.TransactionType ,0 as 'Tolerance_MQty'
from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join (select it.TransactionDT ,it.TransactionSourceGID ,it.ToLocationGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,it.TransactionType ,SUM(it.TargetUnitQuantity) as 'TargetAFOz' ,SUM(it.UnitQuantity) as 'ActualAFOz' from InventoryTransaction it group by it.TransactionDT ,it.TransactionSourceGID ,it.FromLocationGID ,it.FromHistoryLocationGID ,it.ToHistoryLocationGID ,it.ToLocationGID ,it.TransactionType) it on it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID and it.ToLocationGID = fsd.LocationGID
join HistoryLocation fhl on fhl.HistoryLocationGID = it.FromHistoryLocationGID join HistoryLocation thl on thl.HistoryLocationGID = it.ToHistoryLocationGID --join HistoryPen hp on hp.HistoryLocationGID = thl.HistoryLocationGID join HistoryCompany hc on hc.HistoryCompanyGID = thl.HistoryCompanyGID left join [User] u on u.UserGID = fsd.ByUserGID outer apply (select top 1 da.FeedingScheduleDropGID ,da.FeedingScheduleDropAdjustmentGID ,da.AdjustedAFOz ,da.AdjustedDMOz from FeedingScheduleDropAdjustment da where da.FeedingScheduleDropGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID order by da.CreatedDT desc) da ) z where (1=1)
